{"data": {"repository": {"pullRequest": {"id": "MDExOlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0NDA4NjQyMzA2", "number": 1881, "title": "Fixed wing equipment eligibility", "bodyText": "Fixed wing support vehicles are implemented as a subclass of ConventionalFighter, which makes sense for game play purposes, but for construction purposes they are vehicles and have more in common with tanks than aerospace units. This PR corrects the checks used for determining which equipment they can use, basing on the same checks used by other support vehicles and adding fixed wing, airship, and satellite motive types to the the movement mode filtering.\nI also added the checks for MiscType and WeaponType validity to the entity validator for support vehicles and fixed a few other things I noticed while checking the rules. These include rules reference page numbers and switching the environmental sealing in the unit files from the CV version to the SV version.\nThe deleted Partisan Heavy Tank (C3) was a duplicated file. I noticed it when running the entity validator.", "createdAt": "2020-04-24T16:14:48Z", "url": "https://github.com/MegaMek/megamek/pull/1881", "merged": true, "mergeCommit": {"oid": "7b56bd1854e2dd6e3a133a41a31c37bd7f105749"}, "closed": true, "closedAt": "2020-04-25T13:46:17Z", "author": {"login": "neoancient"}, "timelineItems": {"totalCount": 8, "pageInfo": {"startCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpPPAAABcah9--gH2gAyNDA4NjQyMzA2OmU3MDI3NzE1MmQyNTM2ZWM2NGIxZjQ3N2Q3OTRlMjM5ZGM5NzZhODk=", "endCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpPPAAABca0n2NAFqTQwMDEyMzMzNQ==", "hasNextPage": false, "hasPreviousPage": false}, "nodes": [{"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "e70277152d2536ec64b1f477d794e239dc976a89", "author": {"user": {"login": "neoancient", "name": null}}, "url": "https://github.com/MegaMek/megamek/commit/e70277152d2536ec64b1f477d794e239dc976a89", "committedDate": "2020-04-23T19:22:41Z", "message": "Use SV construction rules for checking equipment eligibility for fixed wing SVs."}}, {"__typename": "PullRe